https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XOR_cipher

You can use the xor_cipher(data, key, codetype) function to encrypt and decrypt.
The codetype is an argument to change the output.
Codetype options:
- plaintext -> "str"
- hex list -> "hex"
- binary list -> "bin"

You can use a key of any size as long as it is:
- a divisor of the length of the message

Key / message can be:
- a char
- a string
- a number (lists included)
- a hex (lists included)
- a binary (lists included)